SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 5100
A bill to amend 2008 PA 554, entitled
"Regional convention facility authority act,"
by amending section 11 (MCL 141.1361), as amended by 2009 PA 63.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
