15 the estimated revenue of the authority from all sources for the
16 next fiscal year. The board shall adopt a budget as for the fiscal
17 year in accordance with the uniform budget and accounting act, 1968
18 PA 2, MCL 141.421 to 141.440a.
19 (6) The board shall, by resolution, establish and maintain a
