21 address prior fiscal year shortfalls in distributions under section
22 10(2) of the state convention facility development act, 1985 PA
23 106, MCL 207.630, in the order of priority set forth in section
24 10(2) of the state convention facility development act, 1985 PA
25 106, MCL 207.630. The reserve fund may be funded from distributions
26 to the authority from the convention facility development fund
27 created in section 8 of the state convention facility development
