1 cooperative purchasing agreement with the federal government, this
2 state, or more public entities for the purchase of goods and
3 services necessary at fair and reasonable prices using a
4 competitive procurement method for authority operations.
5 (f) (g) The value of the procurement is less than $5,000.00,
6 and the board has established policies or procedures to ensure that
7 goods or services with a value of less than $5,000.00 are purchased
